name: SipTest
description: Unit tests for the Sip class, focusing on various methods that generate SIP-related data.

test_cases.name: method_returnUpperCaseWithMinimum3Chars
test_cases.description: Tests that the method returns a string with uppercase letters and a minimum length of 3 characters.

test_cases.name: contentType_returnLowerCaseTwoWordsSepereatedBySlashMinimum3And4Chars
test_cases.description: Tests that the contentType method returns a string with two lowercase words separated by a slash, with the first word having a minimum length of 4 characters and the second word having a minimum length of 3 characters.

test_cases.name: messagingPort_return4DigitIntBetween1000And9999
test_cases.description: Tests that the messagingPort method returns a 4-digit integer between 1000 and 9999.

test_cases.name: rtpPort_returnPositiveEvenInt
test_cases.description: Tests that the rtpPort method returns a positive even integer.

test_cases.name: provisionalResponseCode_return3DigitIntBetween100And199

test_cases.name: successResponse_Codereturn3DigitIntBetween200And299
test_cases.description: Tests that the successResponseCode method returns a 3-digit integer between 200 and 299.

test_cases.name: redirectResponseCode_Codereturn3DigitIntBetween300And399
test_cases.description: Tests that the redirectResponseCode method returns a 3-digit integer between 300 and 399.

test_cases.name: clientErrorResponseCode_Codereturn3DigitIntBetween400And499
test_cases.description: Tests that the clientErrorResponseCode method returns a 3-digit integer between 400 and 499.

test_cases.name: serverErrorResponseCode_Codereturn3DigitIntBetween500And599
test_cases.description: Tests that the serverErrorResponseCode method returns a 3-digit integer between 500 and 599.

test_cases.name: globalErrorResponseCode_Codereturn3DigitIntBetween600And699
test_cases.description: Tests that the globalErrorResponseCode method returns a 3-digit integer between 600 and 699.
